title: why cant i buy prehistoric cho?
body: I hear it's a tribute to the new Jurassic world movie that came out and it shows up on his league profile but i cant buy it. it wont allow me.

replies.body: As Keagn mentioned, the Prehistoric skins aren't available to purchase just yet. Not all content is enabled at the beginning of each patch.

why chose to comment on this specific thread that is an easy and obvious one to figure out and answer since its been said many times before instead of in depth questions that would be way more worth the time spent?

I don't think it's particularly obvious to everyone, and some new players may not know. 

I feel like I do answer more in-depth questions when I have the answers. I'm on the skins team, so most of my knowledge lies in that subject, as opposed to gameplay/balance. :]

I think this may be the second time I've beaten you to it Katey P: , but I'm glad to help ^_^

Hey there!

While the Prehistoric skins were implemented in patch 5.11, they have not yet been enabled for purchase. However, they will be up for purchase later on in the patch, so patience is key! ^_^

Hope this helps!
They will most likely be unlocked on Friday, since that is the release date of the Jurassic World movie.
I'd expect them more on Tuesday since that's when they usually put out skins.
